column5: Just wondered what time they were going to draw for raffle? Good luck to all ticket buyers. Joe
c'mon free trip....I sure need one
I've alerted Scott, to remind him that today is June 1st and the day the drawing should happen. He's at the "day job" right now, and will probably be doing it tonight when he gets home.Juls

Uh oh.....my bad.Let me get tickets assigned to the names and I'll get the drawing done this week.I'll video the drawing so everyone know's it's on the up and up and announce the winner.Sorry.....June snuck up on me.Actually I had a fishing tournament this past weekend and just got home this morning......had to donate some money to the winners ya know ;-)
Should be a great trip! The fishing has been crazy so far this year. Big walleyes...
Hope I win But who ever wins, thanks for helping support WC.
